Name: Tina & Rook! Cookie Quest!
About the game: A couple of idiots are hungry for cookies after playing some games! and for some screw-up reason, you have to go through a whole point-and-click puzzle to get that. Will these 2 idiots get to eat their cookies and enjoy their afternoon? Features: a 30 minutes point and click puzzle game to get the cookies. Play as the two idiots trying to get the cookies. Enjoy the wackiness of their interaction along the way. Drag and drop items to solve problems along the way. Create new items by combining 2 items. Accompanied by 2 pieces of music that I had to make despite not having any musical background. There's also a dog.
